{"tid":312764,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成長係 同你講生日快樂嘅人一年比一年少","createTime":"2017-07-07T17:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T09:08:54.000Z","uid":72469,"like":87,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea8d608b9403f61b1c11635fec524149716b6d3","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"小學 爸媽幫我搞生日會<br />\n落手落腳整九大簋<br />\n叫埋姨媽姑姐<br />\n幾十人一齊同我過生日<br />\n<br />\n中學 生日例牌提早幾日book定<br />\n正日同班死黨去唱K<br />\n湊夠五個人免生日人頭費<br />\n唱到一半就會插播明星唱首生日快樂<br />\n食送嘅芝士慕絲蛋糕加支香檳<br />\n此外<br />\n一定有個整蛋糕好難食既朋友<br />\n堅持炮製個難食嘅蛋糕俾你<br />\n<br />\n大學 大學朋友嘅友誼已經唔係中學嗰種親密<br />\n只會whatsapp三粒字hbd<br />\n又或者係個group咁啱有人講起<br />\n就一堆人順便講句hbd 唔會約出黎<br />\n或者過左廿年 生日已經冇咁重要<br />\n<br />\n係中五嗰年開始<br />\n我將所有社交平台嘅生日較左private<br />\n果然呢幾年間<br />\n記得自己生日嘅人 一年比一年少<br />\n<br />\n由琴晚搭正12 我仲期待<br />\n到依家過左12<br />\n除左家人 就得返四句生日快樂<br />\n其中一句仲要係係group有人提起先順便講<br />\n都好嘅 順便講都好過冇講嘛<br />\n<br />\n你地仲記得我生日嗎？<br />\n等我都同自己講聲生日快樂<br />\n咁樣就湊到第五句啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c581b5a56809f328f2de2ae48b6d1253797d158c","tid":312764,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9128d1162c80c11997df79e5185bf6956245622","tid":312764,"uid":51482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128ff9b84c6c271430dbd8ab9feb666531c610d4","tid":312764,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"老咗擺大壽又唔係咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408dd0f3ee7094a584ace3584057db03f374ee36","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"生日可唔可以唔要負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172652ab6ff632464b7cb3e31e33a01c1e6160b6","tid":312764,"uid":83094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"004bd675f31d74b94ed9bd4a954c939f21426ac0","tid":312764,"uid":118810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"生日快樂呀巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96616a616823dbfdb5c2bf0421cf321cc473ce9d","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日啫 冇咩大不了<br />\n咪距離死亡又近一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係生日嘅問題了<br />\n而係有冇人記得你生日<br />\n<br />\n或者係<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇人記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5d33a595a63938b6d5ff833f064f1cf741e96f","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"謝謝以上三句生日快樂<br />\n好耶有八句喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0850d8b40279eca5e0f8bad684fcd3221023fdf3","tid":312764,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"生日快樂！"},{"pid":"6dd1bb27567bd6b888d025acd7ec9fa1b6737ef6","tid":312764,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:42:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7679e67f6ea0a7a5aeb39918d1b18128258c2e9","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大前日我都係得4句生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連最最最最最好朋友都唔記得你生日就真係心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生日快樂<br />\n送第五句俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bbcbdc769bd0b9cfd122bae75707a89c379172","tid":312764,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"951219ebf5e5f1da976be0716916d7e3cb3076aa","tid":312764,"uid":21292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"其中一個原因可能係大個左就未必咁在意生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講句生日快樂有幾難，但真係令你一直快樂既人先緊要"},{"pid":"b0f7cc1ca941bd5e4347242eb1a7f1943a970ce6","tid":312764,"uid":113949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦 慢慢就會習慣 <br />\n人從來都係孤獨"},{"pid":"31fc2c13821ca6e07741bfe52e5d82b10307614c","tid":312764,"uid":113949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"生日快樂 祝日日開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa8b5d48bf8822f0075f0aca31a34243b01795a","tid":312764,"uid":9121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"我都想試下較private <br />\n冇人搵既話會好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97000059e67a858c1747c3a6d2af4aba5d0a8c8","tid":312764,"uid":75773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"其實人數又有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要既係<br />\n你在意既人仲記得你生日<br />\n問題係<br />\n好多我自己明明付出過好多<br />\n又搞生日聚會<br />\n又寫生日卡<br />\n但係最後竟然唔記得左我生日<br />\n可能我一直都係on9仔 所以有好多野已經慣<br />\n試過生日完全無人提<br />\n試過生日反而比狂屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個陣真係幾sad<br />\n心諗 一年得一日 比我開心下得唔得"},{"pid":"fd3d287939e109c5a891913a878de57fd3b8a713","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>^_^<br />\n<br />\n生日要快上，唔可以快落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nching生日快上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都生日快上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8624a99a8fe982a52e66d0c388433a7a25f7b007","tid":312764,"uid":126704,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:03:24.000Z","msg":"生日快樂 <br />\n<br />\n當你以為某d fd一定記得同你講生日快樂 但佢最後都冇講到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個種feeling"},{"pid":"855bfad6616fdd62da97474615e5a27c49da4954","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其中一個原因可能係大個左就未必咁在意生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講句生日快樂有幾難，但真係令你一直快樂既人先緊要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為最親嗰group會同我講嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7672391ac7cb5f32590bfcf673b15f6238fecc3","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁架啦 慢慢就會習慣 <br />\n人從來都係孤獨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知下年仲有冇兩句呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a9f76cc9f2771bb2d35aa8ed2c2cf3e2bfed34","tid":312764,"uid":35245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"生日又咪起身食飯瞓覺<br />\n傻先會期待"},{"pid":"82e7e9838c83444f05b04b820a711c1eab666890","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想試下較private <br />\n冇人搵既話會好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就是 成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0867a505f1418f030fc942f46aa357b40e6faf","tid":312764,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbb50ff52a35fe64b450ab1f13187f29c6ed7c39","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實人數又有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要既係<br />\n你在意既人仲記得你生日<br />\n問題係<br />\n好多我自己明明付出過好多<br />\n又搞生日聚會<br />\n又寫生日卡<br />\n但係最後竟然唔記得左我生日<br />\n可能我一直都係on9仔 所以有好多野已經慣<br />\n試過生日完全無人提<br />\n試過生日反而比狂屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個陣真係幾sad<br />\n心諗 一年得一日 比我開心下得唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣阿巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朋友生日 我都主動約出黎玩<br />\n幫佢地搞聚會<br />\n<br />\n早兩日我約佢地過幾日傾行程<br />\n順便慶祝我生日<br />\n仲有人笑我邊有人會主動叫人慶祝佢生日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後你地有幾多人應約<br />\n又有幾多人記得我生日<br />\n我唔知醜提出埋都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11cd5be7280c8dbdaf35550e686b5ccc281304b","tid":312764,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又捱過一年啦"},{"pid":"b0bacfc2806b59653fea65fbe16cd5d779e11198","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂 <br />\n<br />\n當你以為某d fd一定記得同你講生日快樂 但佢最後都冇講到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個種feeling</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以下年唔會期望<br />\n<br />\n咁就冇失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc73a14c170da2d8d741c6fc474f78545bfe984","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日又咪起身食飯瞓覺<br />\n傻先會期待</blockquote><br />\n唔係期待去邊到玩<br />\n而係有幾多人仲記得自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a03d2ec80d3297a2f8575f486fb76c20a093a2","tid":312764,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"其實有個伴同你講生日快樂開心過一大班人同你講<br />\nbtw 生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0731b78975f142bdd156fd6caa75109d17060849","tid":312764,"uid":72469,"like"