frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47cbfbf0b8bb74b105c39148e13efc811fbf68f","tid":312764,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T21:47:22.000Z","msg":"細細個老母就教我：<br />\n<br />\n「生日只係一年入面另一個普通日子<br />\n冇必要亦唔值得慶祝」<br />\n<br />\n「你都唔使諗住會有禮物<br />\n呢個世界冇免費午餐<br />\n所有野都要自己爭取/賺返嚟<br />\n要得到一樣野你就要付出相應代價」<br />\n<br />\n「想搞生日會？你以為自己係邊個？<br />\n憑咩要人地抽時間嚟同你慶祝生日？<br />\n浪費人地時間好好玩？」<br />\n<br />\n「同人講自己生日幾時搏咩呀？<br />\n搏人地會送野畀你會同你講生日快樂？」<br />\n<br />\n所以一早慣晒冇人會記得自己生日<br />\n當人地本身都唔知嘅時候又點唔記得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩年開始自己都唔係好記得幾時生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<del>屌那星喺鋼煉出嚟之前我就學識 等價交換 呢個道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del>"},{"pid":"06ddc5685b444438a20af83c140d3cc386f8597d","tid":312764,"uid":32786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"故意將自己的存在感較到無限接近0<br />\n所有fd group唔覆（兩三年）<br />\n生日提示熄哂去 <br />\n果然冇人搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c00759322589ed4411719513b3e7d32117b821","tid":312764,"uid":82960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:18:15.000Z","msg":"樓主生日快樂！唔好唔開心<br />\n我都開始習慣 <br />\n有最重要既家人祝福已經足夠"}]}